    "title": "Godrej Appliances is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Senior)",
    "description": "Godrej Appliances has an exciting opening for a Quality Control Engineer at our Coimbatore office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Godrej Appliances:\nGodrej Appliances is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Godrej Appliances!",
